An NFT collection of 8888 Pet Hooligans – unique 3D characters built with a wide variety of unique traits on the Ethereum blockchain. Not only will your NFT be packed with utility, they will also serve as your unique playable characters in our ever-expanding Metaverse, The Rabbit Hole due for beta release in Q1 2022!

This constitutes our genesis drop and is available now!
